origin_prompt.content:
你能够调用以下的API:
[['EnvironmentNews.get_latest_policies', {'name': 'EnvironmentNews.get_latest_policies', 'description': 'Get the latest environmental policies for a given year.', 'required_parameters': [{'name': 'year', 'type': 'STRING', 'description': 'the year for which to get the policies.'}], 'optional_parameters': [], 'return_data': [{'name': 'policies', 'description': 'the list of policies for the given year.'}]}], ['EconomyData.get_environmental_investment', {'name': 'EconomyData.get_environmental_investment', 'description': 'Get the environmental investment data for a given sector and year.', 'required_parameters': [{'name': 'sector', 'type': 'STRING', 'description': 'the sector for which to get the data.'}, {'name': 'year', 'type': 'STRING', 'description': 'the year for which to get the data.'}], 'optional_parameters': [], 'return_data': [{'name': 'investment_data', 'description': 'the environmental investment data for the given sector and year.'}]}], ['CorporateCase.get_environmental_cases', {'name': 'CorporateCase.get_environmental_cases', 'description': 'Get environmental cases for a given industry and year.', 'required_parameters': [{'name': 'industry', 'type': 'STRING', 'description': 'the industry for which to get the cases.'}, {'name': 'year', 'type': 'STRING', 'description': 'the year for which to get the cases.'}], 'optional_parameters': [], 'return_data': [{'name': 'cases', 'description': 'the list of environmental cases for the given industry and year.'}]}], ['CorporateCase.analyze_environmental_effect', {'name': 'CorporateCase.analyze_environmental_effect', 'description': 'Analyze the environmental effect of a given case.', 'required_parameters': [{'name': 'case_id', 'type': 'STRING', 'description': 'the ID of the case to analyze.'}], 'optional_parameters': [], 'return_data': [{'name': 'analysis', 'description': 'the analysis of the environmental effect for the given case.'}]}], ['EnvironmentalAdvice.get_suggestions', {'name': 'EnvironmentalAdvice.get_suggestions', 'description': 'Get suggestions for environmental practices in a given sector.', 'required_parameters': [{'name': 'sector', 'type': 'STRING', 'description': 'the sector for which to get the suggestions.'}], 'optional_parameters': [], 'return_data': [{'name': 'suggestions', 'description': 'the list of suggestions for environmental practices in the given sector.'}]}]]
请生成一个解决用户问题的计划，计划应该是一个行为列表，每个行为的格式如下:

[{
    // 动作的ID
    "id": number;
    // 动作要调用的API名称
    "name": string;
    // 当前API的参数输入(JSON格式)
    "args": "str(Record<string, any>)";
}, ...
]

你可以在计划中想象参数的值，这些指令将按顺序执行。
例如，如果你想调用 `api1` 并传入 `arg1` 和 `arg2`，你可以写下面的计划:

[{
    "id": 0,
    "name": "api1",
    "args": "{'arg1': 'value1', 'arg2': 'value2', ...}",
}, ...
]

这些参数将在执行时被替换为真实的值。请注意，参数应该是一个字符串，而不是一个字典。
请在字典的参数中使用 ''，在其他地方使用 ""，不要打印值为 None 或 null 的参数。

你应该只生成一个 JSON 格式的计划列表。列表应该是完整的计划列表，不要有 `...`。
不要生成任何解释 JSON 的文本。
